Menyelamatkan hidup Anda?  Kapan?

00:19:02.600 --> 00:19:03.600
Kapan?

00:19:03.760 --> 00:19:07.760
Saat... Saat aku pingsan,

00:19:08.520 --> 00:19:09.640
Anda...

